08/17/80	argument_list.compin

Syntax:  .ifi argument_list
     OR  .ifi arg_list


Function:
This macro emits an argument list label and prepares for a list of
arguments.


Macro action:
1) inserts 24pt. of white space
2) emits the label "ARGUMENTS" in 10pt Helvetica Bold Italic flush
   left, followed by white space appropriate for the device
3) sets the text indentation to the second level in preparation for the
   list of arguments (see argument.compin.info concerning generation of
   the arguments)

(END)
